headline: Intel Could Still Be a Big Winner in the AI Server Boom
summary: Server sales are booming, largely thanks to artificial intelligence (AI) server demand.  Intel isn't a major player in the AI accelerator market, but its server CPU business can benefit from strong server demand.  Demand for artificial intelligence (AI) infrastructure is off the charts.
